          <p style="font-size:0.8rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">A <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/" target="_blank" style="color:var(--gold-light);">Lakeshore Gift</a> resource.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Guides</h4>
